네트워크 계층(1)

1. Network Layer
 (1) 기능
  - transport segement from sending to receiving host
  - on sending side encapsulates segements into datagrams
  - on receiving side, delivers segements to trasnport layer
  - network layer protocols in every host, router
  - router examines header
  
 (2) interplay between routing and forwarding(in router)
  - destination <-> forwarding table entry 매치시켜서 전송
  - routing : forwarding table을 만드는 것
  - 주소 범위로 관리됨(longest prefix matching)
